          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Chicagoland's top provider for fences, playgrounds, basketball courts, and trampolines.",
            "text": "<p>Fenceworks is the leading company in the Chicagoland area for all your fence, playground, basketball, and trampoline needs. The business was started in 1967 by Stan Ascher, “The Guy on 41.” Stan, along with the Fenceworks family, Lindsey and Sandy are here to provide you with all the quality service, selection, and value you expect from Fenceworks. Our Fence department has provided thousands of yards everywhere with beauty, privacy, and security. All the products in our <a href=\"/collections/play-sets\" title=\"Play Sets\">Playground</a>, <a href=\"/collections/basketball-hoops\" title=\"Basketball Hoops\">Basketball</a>, and <a href=\"https://theguyon41.com/pages/trampolines\" title=\"Trampoline\">Trampoline</a> departments were carefully selected with your child’s safety in mind, as well as offer the best products in the industry. We welcome you to visit our indoor showroom! We pride ourselves in giving you, the customer, all our knowledge and professionalism that you have come to expect.</p>",
            "align": "left",
            "width": "1/2"
          }
        },
